graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.27+<br/>Required]
    DSPO -->|workflow execution| Argo[Argo Workflows 3.x<br/>Embedded namespace-scoped]
    DSPO -->|artifact storage| S3Storage[S3-Compatible Storage<br/>Required - Minio or External]
    DSPO -->|metadata storage| MySQLDB[MySQL-Compatible Database<br/>Required - MariaDB or External]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    DSPO -.->|enhanced features| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.11+<br/>Optional - Routes, OAuth]
    DSPO -.->|DSPv1 only| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines - Tekton 1.8+<br/>Optional - DSPv1 only]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Route/API]
    DSPO -->|authentication| OAuthService[OpenShift OAuth<br/>OAuth2 Proxy]
    DSPO -->|TLS certificates| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>Certificate generation]
    DSPO -->|metrics collection| Prometheus[User Workload Monitoring<br/>ServiceMonitor]
    DSPO -.->|network policies| ODHMonitoring[ODH Monitoring Stack<br/>NetworkPolicy authorized]

    %% External Services
    DSPO -->|image pulls| Registry[Container Registry<br/>Quay, registry.redhat.io]

    %% Component Details
    subgraph "Optional Components"
        MariaDB[MariaDB 10.3+<br/>Default DB]
        Minio[Minio<br/>Default S3]
        ExternalS3[External S3<br/>AWS S3, etc.]
        ExternalDB[External MySQL<br/>RDS, Cloud SQL]
    end

    S3Storage -.->|can be| Minio
    S3Storage -.->|can be| ExternalS3
    MySQLDB -.->|can be| MariaDB
    MySQLDB -.->|can be| ExternalDB

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
